will bring them out.

124
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:21,000
Elhemdulillah silametî gihişt vir o. Mala Xwedê ava be.
Teb'an post bi reqem e, her kes otê, paşê, meylî xwa de
feqîro.
 
Praise be to God safety reached here. May God bless them. Of
