Uncle, the leader of the dance must sing, what can he say.

157
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,000
Ne wele nizanim.
 
No by God I don't know.

158
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:45,000
Bese ev sargo vinda, xala mîn yek kela ma... cigo nîwa re,
